封城之下，湖北黄石真实影像记录 | 三明治。
Beneath the city, Hubei Yellowstone's real - life image records & # 124; & # 45; sandwiches.
卡斯。
Kass.
三明治                      。
Sandwiches.
三明治。
Sandwiches.
一个鼓励你把生活写出来的平台。
A platform to encourage you to write about your life.
成立于2011年3月，旗下设有三明治写作学院，以及媒体平台“中国三明治”，同时致力于将故事跨界应用于产品设计、城市文化挖掘、展览市集、空间打造等立体场域。
Founded in March 2011, it has a sandwich writing academy and a media platform, "Chinese Sandwiches," and is committed to cross-border application of stories in product design, urban culture excavation, exhibition fairs, and space-building.
。
.
卡斯的老家在湖北黄石，因疫情封城之后，他用镜头记录了在这个城市里偶然还能见到的身影：驻守要道的执勤人员、送外卖的小哥、逆行而上的志愿者和戴着口罩在江堤上跑步的人群。
Kass, whose home is in Huangshi, Hubei province, used the footage to chronicle the occasional presence in the city: manning the main thoroughfare, delivering takeaway brothers, retrograde volunteers, and people running on river banks wearing masks.
除此之外，在镜头里出现更多的是无言的建筑、封锁的通道。
In addition, in the lens there are more wordless buildings, blockades of the passage.
作者：卡斯坐标：湖北 黄石职业：抖音编剧一边和浩浩江水，一边是彼此相连的黄石和鄂州。
Authors: Hubei Yellowstone career: Shadow writer and Haohao River, on the one hand, Yellowstone and Hubei Province, on the other.
疫情发生之前，很多鄂州花湖和杨叶镇的人在黄石买了房子，也有黄石人因花湖和杨叶镇的房子便宜在那边买了房子。
Before the outbreak, many people in Huahu and Yangye towns in Huizhou bought houses in Yellowstone, while others in Yellowstone bought houses in Huahu and Yangye at low cost.
两边来往密切，因距离黄石城区比到鄂州城区要近，为了方便两地人员交通来往，黄石开通了三路公交汽车来往花湖。
In order to facilitate the traffic between the two places, Huang Shi opened a three-way bus to and from Huahu Lake.
现如今因守土有责，守土担责，守土尽责的明确规定，两城各自委派人员拉起铁丝网和档板沿界驻守，那边的过不来，这边的也无法过去。
Now, due to the responsibility of the earth, the responsibility of the clear compliance with the earth, the two cities have appointed personnel to pull up the barbed wire and fence along the boundary, the other can not cross, this side can not cross.
沿江堤坝的旁边是长江公路二桥，连接黄石与黄冈，过去车辆穿梭，现如今已很少再看到车辆通行，唯一看到车辆经过的是装运物资的货车，从黄冈方向开往黄石。
Along the river dyke is the Yangtze River Highway Bridge, connecting Yellowstone and Huanggang, used to shuttle vehicles, now rarely seen traffic, the only vehicle to see goods trucks, from the direction of Huang Gang to Yellowstone.
要知道跨过长江二桥经过黄石就是武汉，那里正是爆发疫情的暴风眼，弹药正源源不断通过这座斜挎大桥源源不断地运送到暴风中心。
The crossing of the Yangtze River through Yellowstone is known as Wuhan, the epicenter of the storm, and ammunition is constantly flowing through the sloping bridge to the centre of the storm.
在这里执勤的同学告诉我，鄂州杨叶那边和黄石完全隔断通路后，很多人不听劝，想方设法绕着弯往黄石这边跑。
The students who are on duty here told me that many people didn't listen to the advice and tried to run around the bend to Yellowstone.
有人半夜摸黑趁着工作人员不注意翻过铁隔板来黄石，当然结果还是被发现直接拘留，有人半夜靠路熟骑共享单车从田间野地绕行到黄石江边再上岸，更有甚者在杨叶那边滑着木船，从杨叶绕过管制到黄石，被黄石防疫指挥部的工作人员看到后明令要求劝返，他却不听，继续往前滑，直到在你看不见、追不上的地方登陆上岸。
He was found directly detained in the middle of the night by road riders sharing bikes from the fields to the banks of the Yellowstone River. What's more, he took a wooden boat on the other side of the poplar leaves, circumvented the controls to Yellowstone, and refused to listen until he landed where you couldn't see or catch up.
不明白这些民众为什么非要违抗规定。
I don't understand why these people have to disobey the rules.
其实最不听劝导的就是那些独自居住的老大爷，他们本身的退休金又少，又没人照顾，还没文化，不懂知识也不看新闻。
In fact, the last to listen to advice is those who live alone, their own pensions are small, no care, no education, no knowledge, no news.
最关键的是他们不怕死，不怕被病毒感染。
The most important thing is that they are not afraid of death and infection.
同学告诉我那些老头平常散步、晒太阳惯了，以前什么大风大浪没有见到过，都没有出问题，种的菜地就在杨叶那边，他非要过去那边，你不让他过去试试看。
My classmate told me that the old men used to go for a walk and get used to the sun. There had been no waves of any kind before.
这些可怜又无助还蛮不讲理的老年人，他们会拿出平常吃的药吓唬执勤的人员，很多人拿他们没有办法。
Poor, helpless and unreasonable old men, they would give their usual medicine to frighten the men on duty, and many would have nothing to do with them.
还好我同学是个强硬派，依法执行公务，特殊时期不论男女老少只要违规违法，就会依法惩处。
Fortunately, my classmate is a hard-line, in accordance with the law, men, women and children in special periods as long as violations of the law will be punished.
他们并不清楚要值守到什么时候也不清楚会遇到什么突发情况，但大家都有个共同的心愿，祈盼疫情能够快点结束。
They don't know when they're going to be on duty, and they don't know what's going to happen, but they all have a common desire that the epidemic end soon.
同学告诉我等到疫情结束他希望能够放个长假，体验下我们天天宅在家里父母的感受，吃了睡，睡了吃，然后玩个养成类的游戏，这样的日子应该也不错。
My classmate told me that it would be nice to wait until the epidemic was over and he wanted to take a long vacation, to experience how our parents felt when we were home every day, to eat, to sleep, to eat, and to play a game of nurture.
时间不早了，就在我即将和同学告别前碰到一个人，开着一个装水产品的车将车开到限行路口，他从车里下来拿了一个红色塑料袋找交警搭话。
It was late, just before I took leave of my classmate, I met a man driving a car with aquatic products to a restricted road junction. He got out of the car and took a red plastic bag to answer the policeman.
而后他走到堤防执勤点，我同学告诉他不能再过去了，他说他闺女住在那边，吃的东西没有了，买了点菜想给他闺女送过去。
Then he went to the embankment and was told by my classmate that he could not go on. He said his daughter lived there, had nothing to eat, and bought something to take to his daughter.
同学告诉他这里已经全部封死了，根据规定人过不去，东西也过不去。
Students told him that here has been completely sealed, according to the regulations can not pass, things can not pass.
他给闺女打电话，她闺女告诉他可以从旁边小道绕行，他挂断电话后同学告诉他那边的通道也全部封死，并且有人把守，不可能过得去，劝他原路返回。
He called his daughter, who told him that he could take a detour from the side lane. When he hung up the phone, he was told that the passageway over there was also blocked and there was no way to get through.
看到他站在原地远望铁档板对面，心有念想却又无能为力的样子，心情十分失落。
See him standing there looking at the iron baffle opposite, thinking but helpless appearance, the mood is very frustrated.
现在特殊时期没有公交，的士也不会开过来，只有走到原来的老客运站才能看到的士。
Now there is no public transport in special period, taxi will not come, only to walk to the original old passenger station can see the taxi.
途中看到了送外卖的小哥、逆行而上的志愿者和戴着口罩在江堤上跑步的人群。
On the way to see the delivery of the younger brother, retrograde volunteers and wearing masks on the river bank running on the crowd.
希望目前空荡的街道、无人没车的马路和失去嘈杂叫卖声的市场可以尽快恢复生机。
Hopefully, the empty streets, the empty streets and the noisy, noisy markets will be restored to life as soon as possible.
今天下午又出了一趟门，本来是去区政府找同学聊聊黄石西塞山区现在的疫情状况，因不敢再坐的士，沿途步行2.2公里，途中拍摄了许多照片。
This afternoon I went out to the district government to talk to my classmate about the current epidemic situation in the Hessian Mountains. I dared not take a taxi again.
被封死的各个路口、各个社区、各条通道。
The blockaded intersections, the communities, the corridors.
用包围建筑垃圾的蓝白布条将客运站包围了起来，再用供水抢修防护栏隔绝小区出入口。
The terminal is surrounded by a blue-and-white strip of cloth surrounding the building's waste, which is then sealed off from access to the community by water-supply barriers.
用席梦思挡住出口，隔绝病毒。
Use Simmons to block the exit and isolate the virus.
号称永不歇业的超市和KFC。
Supermarkets and KFC, which claim never to be closed.
值守在小区、社区、临时菜市场的一线工作人员。
Duty in the community, community, temporary food market front-line workers.
唯一可以进出通行，但需登记出入的社区执勤点。
Only accessible, but registered community access points.
封城中城市里的一抹亮色——环卫工人。
A bright color in the city - sanitation workers.
疫情中没有生意的门店。
A store with no business in the epidemic.
疫情中解决人们生活物资问题，超市、水果、食品和蛋糕店生意都还不错。
Supermarkets, fruit, food and confectionery are doing well in dealing with the problem of people living in the epidemic.
黄石市中心街道武汉路客运站对面形成了一个露天菜市场，多数卖菜的商户是从旁边的富豪集贸市场搬过来的，菜价根据当天的供应量一天一变，目前茄子涨到了10元一斤，花菜6元一斤，香菇15一斤，红菜苔7元一斤都比年前的价格要高出了许多。
Huangshi central street Wuhan Road passenger terminal opposite the formation of an open-air vegetable market, most of the merchants selling vegetables from the nearby rich market, prices change daily according to the supply of the day, the current eggplant rose to 10 yuan a catty, cauliflower 6 yuan a catty, mushroom 15 catty, red cauliflower 7 yuan a catty than a year ago price.
消毒清洁员在消杀。
The disinfectant cleaners are killing.
疫情中最好用的交通工具就是自行车，骑车人：整个马路都是我的。
The best means of transportation in an epidemic situation is bicycles. Cyclists: The whole road is mine.
黄石收治隔离观察的酒店。
Yellowstone inpatient quarantined hotel.
疫情中还在出门的人，大多数是买物资、送物资。
The epidemic is still out of the people, most of the goods, deliveries.
独属于两人的街道。
The only street belonging to two people.
上海生煎包门店旁楼与楼之间透出了一束光，有光的地方就有希望，有了希望便有了力量。
There is a beam of light between the side building and the building. Where there is light, there is hope; when there is hope, there is strength.
